Test Case 1 (Positive)
1. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login -> page opened
2. Enter valid credentials (Student, 909090) -> Entered
3. Click "Вход" button -> http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/ page is opened. Student_37 username is displayed in top right header

Test Case 2 (Positive)
Preconditions: - user is logged in

1. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/ -> page opened
2. Click on username from top right corner -> user details pop-up is displayed
3. Click "Выход" button -> user is redirected to login page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login

Test Case 3 (Negative)
1. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login -> page opened
2. Enter invalid password (Student, 9090909) -> Entered
3. Click "Вход" button -> user is not logged in. http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login page is opened. Password field cleared
4. Repeat steps 2-3 for invalid Email(name) -> user is not logged in. http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/login page is opened. Password field cleared

Test Case 4 (Positive)
Preconditions: - user is logged in

1. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/ -> page opened
2. Click on username from top right corner -> user details pop-up is displayed
3. Click "Профиль" button -> Profile details are displayed
4. Check profile details  -> email: i1nfo@qalight.com, user: Student_37, login: Student, pswrd fields are empty

Test Case 5 (Positive)
Preconditions: - user is logged in

1. Open page http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/ -> page opened
2. Navigate to "Сделки" from left nav menu -> "Сделки" page (http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal) is opened
3. Click "+" button from top right corner -> http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal/edit page is opened
4. Fill in all required fields and click "Создать" button -> "Сделки" page (http://v3.test.itpmgroup.com/deal) is opened with all available deals
5. Check already created deal -> Deal is displayed with all previously entered data

